data.description: This 4 bedroom and 2 full bath home features a large fenced in private yard on the water to enjoy your morning coffee or evening sunsets.  It boasts an open floor plan with a lot of natural light. The kitchen has a center island with counter seating, pendant lighting, upgraded granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances. The primary bedroom overlooks the water and offers a spacious walk-in closet and bathroom with dual granite vanities and large walk-in shower. There is also a 2 car garage and lush landscaping surrounding the property. It is located in the desirable gated community of Copperstone where HOA fees are low and includes your internet and cable. The amenities include a resort style pool and clubhouse, fitness center and playground.  This convenient location is close to beaches, shopping, golf, restaurants, airports and medical centers. Schedule your showing today.
